## The Review Loop (Chapter-Level)

For every completed chapter draft, run this loop before moving to the next:

```
CHAPTER REVIEW LOOP
─────────────────────────────────────────────
Step 1 — Red Team          (red-team-critic)
  Focus:  Logical flaws, weak arguments, fluff
  Output: Annotated critique + fixes required

Step 2 — Beta Read         (beta-reader-simulator)
  Focus:  Reader experience, confusion, disengagement
  Output: Persona reactions + confusion map

Step 3 — Journey Map       (reader-journey-mapper)
  Focus:  Engagement score for this chapter
  Output: Hook/delivery/exit scores + risk flags

Step 4 — Address Findings
  Route:  Evidence gaps → research-evidence-builder
  Route:  Structural problems → chapter-builder rewrite
  Route:  All craft fixes → editor-sharpener

Step 5 — Deep Edit         (editor-sharpener)
  Focus:  Prose quality using review briefs from Steps 1–3
  Output: Polished chapter + Edit Log

Step 6 — Update Status
  Mark chapter ✅ Complete in Book Project State
─────────────────────────────────────────────
```

